SUMMARY:Brunch at Simply Crepes
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\nJoin us for a Sunday brunch at Simply Crepes at the North Raleigh location.\nSpots are **first come\, first served**. If your plans change\, please reach out **at least 24 hours in advance** so someone else can join.\nEvent Date: March 15\nGuest Count: 6
