SUMMARY:Exchange Family Center Presents: 3rd Annual Bull City Pickleball Classic
DESCRIPTION:Discover Durham Together\n***Event is not free***\n(https://app.pickleballden.com/external-tournament/1647782)\n\nHello everyone\,\n\nIf you didn't know when I am not planning events here\, I plan events for work\, lol.\n\nThat being said\, the nonprofit I work with and I are hosting a fundraiser in the form of a Pickleball tournament! Registration opened this morning and I wanted to get the word out. If you like pickleball or enjoy supporting a local Durham charity you should consider entering\, donating\, or just coming to spectate.\n\nTournament fee is $50\nand each additional bracket is $10\n\nIf you have any more specific questions\, feel free to message me personally or leave a comment!\n\nHope to see you there!\n\n##
